name: Truffle Grilled Cheese
description: Studying is exhausting. So recover with Mana’s Truffled Grilled Cheese! Pamper yourself with a luxurious earthy truffle flavor that perfectly complements Mana’s melty cheese blend.

name: Chicken Parmesan
description: Fried chicken for the win! Mama’s chicken parmesan is a marriage of textures and flavors. You’ll love every bite of the succulent, crunchy chicken chunks sprinkled generously with real parmesan cheese in between slices of soft bread.

name: Sailor's Salmon
description: Need a light refreshing bite to beat the tropical heat? The Sailor’s Salmon sandwich with grilled salmon, sliced cucumbers, and sweet sour sauce will definitely cool you off!

name: Pesto Paradise
description: Plain grilled cheese is awesome. Add pesto and it becomes paradise! Take a bite of Mana’s delicious mix of cheese mix coupled with its in-house pesto for a taste of heaven.
